  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Evil monsters are trying to invade the last remaining village!</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are 5 areas near the village, and you will receive a reward each time you clear an area : Forest, Coast, Grave, Glacier, Hell</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Advance to the next area by clearing various bosses that block movement to the next area.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You need powerful items to deal with powerful bosses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Using the gold earned during the adventure, you can return to the village and acquire powerful equipment through gambling or strengthen items using strengthening items.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The adventure doesn't end when you become the town's hero with just one class. Share valuable items acquired during your adventure using the public warehouse.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Even now, Last Town is waiting for a new hero.</strong></i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Character Custom</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can design hair, hair color, skin color, eyes, eyebrows, mouth, and beard as you like</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3513050/extras/2736f95335ff22432137592fb41ef9b5.avif?t=1740935256\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3513050/extras_big/2736f95335ff22432137592fb41ef9b5.avif?t=1740935256 width=800 height=183 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Character Class</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 character class : Rogue, Warrior, Paladin</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Different wear items, ability, passive , and 7 skills for each class</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3513050/extras/95586f2a53477319a3b558d65a60f23e.avif?t=1740935256\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3513050/extras_big/95586f2a53477319a3b558d65a60f23e.avif?t=1740935256 width=800 height=182 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3513050/extras/6b02257c522ce55c41aa9817b893dab1.avif?t=1740935256\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3513050/extras_big/6b02257c522ce55c41aa9817b893dab1.avif?t=1740935256 width=800 height=182 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Item</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The types of items that can be equipped are different for each class</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Item levels are divided into Normal, Magic, Rare, Unique, and Legend, and each item ability is added to Magic level or higher</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get items from adventures or tavern gambling and upgrade them at the Forge</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3513050/extras/222627847aeba309cbdbce4e6f3edd16.avif?t=1740935256\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3513050/extras_big/222627847aeba309cbdbce4e6f3edd16.avif?t=1740935256 width=800 height=182 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Area</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Clear the boss of each map and move on to the next area</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once you conquer a region, you will receive a regional reward when you successfully return to your adventure</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3513050/extras/f24b8bfb043295a5d7350adad86f31fb.avif?t=1740935256\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3513050/extras_big/f24b8bfb043295a5d7350adad86f31fb.avif?t=1740935256 width=800 height=182 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Evil monsters are trying to invade the last remaining village!</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are 5 areas near the village, and you will receive a reward each time you clear an area : Forest, Coast, Grave, Glacier, Hell</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Advance to the next area by clearing various bosses that block movement to the next area.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You need powerful items to deal with powerful bosses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Using the gold earned during the adventure, you can return to the village and acquire powerful equipment through gambling or strengthen items using strengthening items.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The adventure doesn't end when you become the town's hero with just one class. Share valuable items acquired during your adventure using the public warehouse.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Even now, Last Town is waiting for a new hero.</strong></i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Character Custom</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can design hair, hair color, skin color, eyes, eyebrows, mouth, and beard as you like</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3513050/extras/2736f95335ff22432137592fb41ef9b5.avif?t=1740935256\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3513050/extras_big/2736f95335ff22432137592fb41ef9b5.avif?t=1740935256 width=800 height=183 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Character Class</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 character class : Rogue, Warrior, Paladin</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Different wear items, ability, passive , and 7 skills for each class</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3513050/extras/95586f2a53477319a3b558d65a60f23e.avif?t=1740935256\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3513050/extras_big/95586f2a53477319a3b558d65a60f23e.avif?t=1740935256 width=800 height=182 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3513050/extras/6b02257c522ce55c41aa9817b893dab1.avif?t=1740935256\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3513050/extras_big/6b02257c522ce55c41aa9817b893dab1.avif?t=1740935256 width=800 height=182 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Item</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The types of items that can be equipped are different for each class</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Item levels are divided into Normal, Magic, Rare, Unique, and Legend, and each item ability is added to Magic level or higher</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get items from adventures or tavern gambling and upgrade them at the Forge</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3513050/extras/222627847aeba309cbdbce4e6f3edd16.avif?t=1740935256\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3513050/extras_big/222627847aeba309cbdbce4e6f3edd16.avif?t=1740935256 width=800 height=182 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Area</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Clear the boss of each map and move on to the next area</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once you conquer a region, you will receive a regional reward when you successfully return to your adventure</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3513050/extras/f24b8bfb043295a5d7350adad86f31fb.avif?t=1740935256\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3513050/extras_big/f24b8bfb043295a5d7350adad86f31fb.avif?t=1740935256 width=800 height=182 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
